[Subagent Task]: # D&D Remodel — Agent 2: Frontend Layout + CSS Rewrite

Complete rewrite of ~/dnd-app/frontend/index.html structure and ~/dnd-app/frontend/styles.css.

## Read First
- ~/dnd-app/frontend/index.html (current 1852 lines)
- ~/dnd-app/frontend/styles.css (current 6130 lines)
- ~/dnd-app/ULTRAPLAN-REMODEL.md (the full plan)

## CRITICAL: Understand the Current JS
The current index.html has a `<script src="/dnd/app.js">` or inline JS that references specific DOM element IDs. You need to PRESERVE all critical IDs that the JS references, or the app will break. Read the JS carefully and keep all IDs that are used.

Actually — check if there's a separate app.js:
```bash
ls ~/dnd-app/frontend/*.js
```
If not, the JS is inline in index.html. In that case, keep ALL the JS code but restructure the HTML around it.

## New HTML Structure

Replace the current sidebar-based layout with a bottom-tab layout:

```html
