## New styles.css — Complete Rewrite

Replace the 6130-line CSS with a clean Apex Dark + Amber system:

### Color Tokens
```css
:root {
  --bg: #0d121b;
  --bg-surface: #0f141f;
  --bg-card: #131a27;
  --bg-hover: rgba(212, 167, 58, 0.05);
  --bg-active: rgba(212, 167, 58, 0.08);
  --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  --border-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
  --text: #c9d1d9;
  --text-bright: #f3f4f6;
  --text-muted: #6e7681;
  --text-dim: #424854;
  --gold: #d4a73a;
  --gold-dim: rgba(212, 167, 58, 0.4);
  --gold-bg: rgba(212, 167, 58, 0.08);
  --success: #86efac;
  --danger: #fca5a5;
  --warning: #fde047;
  --font-display: 'Cinzel', serif;
  --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  --radius: 10px;
  --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
}
```

### Key CSS Components
```css
/* Grid texture background */
body::before { content:''; position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.024) 1px, transparent 1px),
  linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.024) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 48px 48px; }

/* Bottom tab bar */
.bottom-tabs { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 64px;
  background: var(--bg-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; z-index: 50; padding-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0); }
.tab-btn { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  justify-content: center; gap: 2px; background: none; border: none;
  color: var(--text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; cursor: pointer; }
.tab-btn.active { color: var(--gold); }
.tab-icon { font-size: 22px; }

/* Tab content */
.tab-content { position: fixed; top: 44px; bottom: 64px; left: 0; right: 0; overflow: hidden; }
.tab-pane { display: none; height: 100%; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }
.tab-pane.active { display: block; }

/* Panel overlay */
.panel-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 100; background: var(--bg);
  transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease); }
.panel-overlay.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.panel-header { height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.panel-back { background: none; border: none; color: var(--gold); font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; }
.panel-body { height: calc(100% - 44px); overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }

/* App header */
.app-header { height: 44px; background: var(--bg-surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 16px; gap: 12px; font-size: 12px; }

/* Onboarding */
.onboard { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  min-height: 100vh; padding: 24px; }
.onboard-hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.onboard-icon { font-size: 80px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.onboard-hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 32px; color: var(--gold); }
.onboard-hero p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px; }
.onboard-buttons { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; width: 100%; max-width: 320px; }
.big-btn { padding: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid; text-align: center; }
.big-btn.gold { background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212,167,58,0.15), rgba(212,167,58,0.08));
  border-color: var(--gold-dim); color: var(--gold); }
.big-btn.outline { background: transparent; border-color: var(--border-strong); color: var(--text); }
.big-btn.ghost { background: transparent; border-color: transparent; color: var(--text-muted); }

/* Cards */
.card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px; }

/* Scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(212,167,58,0.15); border-radius: 4px; }
```

### Tab Switching JS (add to the script section)
```javascript
function switchTab(tabId) {
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-pane').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
  document.getElementById('tab-' + tabId)?.classList.add('active');
  document.querySelector(`.tab-btn[data-tab="${tabId}"]`)?.classList.add('active');
}

function openPanel(title, contentHtml) {
  document.getElementById('panel-title').textContent = title;
  document.getElementById('panel-body').innerHTML = contentHtml;
  const overlay = document.getElementById('panel-overlay');
  overlay.style.display = 'block';
  requestAnimationFrame(() => overlay.classList.add('open'));
}

function closePanel() {
  const overlay = document.getElementById('panel-overlay');
  overlay.classList.remove('open');
  setTimeout(() => { overlay.style.display = 'none'; }, 300);
}
```

## CRITICAL Rules
- KEEP all existing DOM element IDs that JS references (login-pin, enter-game-btn, show-create-btn, etc.)
- KEEP all existing JS code — just restructure the HTML around it
- Remove the old sidebar (#sidebar and all nav-*-btn elements) — remap to bottom tabs
- Remove MAGI sidebar (the Apex nav from parent app — remove <div id="nav"></div> and renderNav calls)
- Add Google Fonts link for Cinzel: `<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">`
- The tab-play, tab-party, tab-ai, tab-more divs are PLACEHOLDERS — Agent 3 and 4 will fill them
- Your job is the STRUCTURE, LAYOUT, CSS, and TAB SYSTEM only
- Test HTML structure is balanced

